Package com.facebook.buck.jvm.java.plugin.api

Class TaskEventMirror

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.jvm.java.plugin.api.TaskEventMirror
  • public final class TaskEventMirror
extends Object
    TaskEvent is included with the compiler and is thus not directly accessible from within Buck's class loader. This class is used as a mirror within Buck's class loader for a TaskEvent within the compiler's.
